headline: Henry Schein to Webcast Third Quarter 2025 Conference Call on Tuesday, November 4, 2025, at 8:00 A.M. ET
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., October 21, 2025--Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC), the world’s largest provider of health care solutions to office-based dental and medical practitioners, announced today that it will release its third quarter 2025 financial results before the stock market opens on Tuesday, November 4, 2025, and will provide a live webcast of its earnings conference call on the same day beginning at 8:00 a.m. Eastern time.
